name: G.O.A.T. 🐐
description:
Hip hop music, commonly known as rap music, is a popular music genre that originated in the United States. Assume you want to be a rapper. Can you keep up with the beat? Can you rhyming be rhythmic? Do you have feelings and thoughts? Rappers that are great speak from the heart, repeat their message, and can rhyme, flow, and ride the rhythm. Learn from your favourite rappers and deep dive into the world of rap.
